=== New developer features in 1.47 ===
* (T389281) The Language and LocalisationCache classes now support using the
  Leximorph library. Language supports Leximorph for grammar, plural, gender,
  formality, and bidi transformations, which also affects parser functions that
  use these Language methods. LocalisationCache supports loading plural rules
  from Leximorph. When $wgUseLeximorph is enabled, these features use
  Leximorph's modular handlers instead of the legacy implementations and
  plural-rule files.
* …

